version_description:
Experience the new app by P4P!

As always, we ask you to report any BUG via email to support@passion4profession.net, before leaving any negative reviews. We will be happy to reply as quickly as possible and fix any BUG that you report to us. We work hard to give you the best product possible, because working out should be a pleasure ;-)

P4P Team

Are you having a hard time losing weight and burning off excess calories? This is the perfect App for you!
Choose how many calories you want to burn and start exercising right away, one click is enough!

Does your diet say it's time to snack on a banana (100 calories) and do you want to burn the calories consumed right away? Choose a 100-calorie exercise session and start burning the calories right away!

Do you need a long-term plan to associate to your diet to burn x amount of calories per week and per month?
Choose one of our plans to reach your goals, sign up, and make a commitment to reach your desired results. 

FREE EXERCISE SESSIONS

BURN 50 CALORIES IN 6 MINUTES

BURN 100 CALORIES IN 13 MINUTES

ANTI-CELLULITE EXERCISE FOR YOUR LEGS - BURN 70 CALORIES IN 8 MINUTES

RED-HOT ABDOMINAL EXERCISES - BURN 70 CALORIES IN 6 MINUTES

And much more…

COMPLETE LONG-TERM EXERCISE PLANS (paid)

1000 CALORIES WEEKLY ( 8 weeks)
Burn 1000 calories each week, with a different exercise session every day to reach your goal.

MORNING METABOLISM BOOST ( 6 weeks)
Science says that aerobic exercise early in the morning, even for a few minutes, pushes your metabolism to the limit; try this plan and check it yourself! 

If you've read enough, download the App for free and try it. Talk is cheap, you burn calories by moving around ;-) 

As always, we ask you to report any BUG via email to support@passion4profession.net, before leaving any negative reviews. We will be happy to reply as quickly as possible and fix any BUG that you report to us. We work hard to give you the best product possible, because working out should be a pleasure ;-)
